From: haddix (Rita Hanson)
Subject: lseek/O_APPEND
Index: lib 4.2BSD

   Doing an lseek() on a file that has been opened with O_APPEND does
not return an error.
   All writes, however, will be appended to the end of the file.  So, the
lseek() has no effect.
                                Rita
